headline: Nvidia says two mystery customers accounted for 39% of Q2 revenue
summary: Nearly 40% of Nvidia’s second quarter revenue came from just two companies, identified in a filing as "Customer A" and "Customer B."

headline: Will 2025's 3 Best-Performing "Ten Titans" Stocks Lead the Group Again in 2026?
summary: Oracle, Netflix, and Nvidia are up more than 35% year to date, adding to their outsized gains in recent years.
